column1: Observer H Rothery was a gardener and the Misses Wrigley (he observed for them) lived at Ibbotsholme, Troutbeck. This is at NY402005, 150'
However, Ibbotsholme is too far from Ambleside church which is 1 mile north on the record.
A Henry Rothery, gardener, lived at Stagshaw Cottage in 1911, domestic gardener
Stagshaw Cottage is at NY379028 about 1 mile south of Ambleside church and the right elevation so NGR for that
